'''威廉·佛塞'''（'''William Forsythe'''，{{bd|1955年|6月7日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]演員。他最出名是在電影中飾演不同的黑幫和硬漢，例如《[[撫養亞利桑那|撫養亞利桑那]]》、《[[四海兄弟|四海兄弟]]》、《{{link-en|九反威龍 (1991年電影)|Stone Cold (1991 film)|九反威龍}}》、《{{link-en|邊緣煞星|Out for Justice}}》、《{{link-en|五個殺手的傳說|Things to Do in Denver When You're Dead}}》、《[[至尊神探|至尊神探]]》、《[[石破天驚|石破天驚]]》、《{{link-en|黑幫大時代|American Me}}》和《[[獵殺猛鬼公路|獵殺猛鬼公路]]》。他也在電視劇《[[酒私風雲|酒私風雲]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/boardwalk-empire-adds-william-forsythe-182300 |title = 'Boardwalk Empire' Adds William Forsythe as Gangster for Season 2 (Exclusive) |author = Lacey Rose |date = 2011-04-26 |publisher = The Hollywood Reporter |language = en |access-date = 2018-08-27 |archive-date = 2020-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200303002318/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/boardwalk-empire-adds-william-forsythe-182300 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://collider.com/william-forsythe-charlie-cox-boardwalk-empire/ |title = William Forsythe and Charlie Cox Join the Second Season of BOARDWALK EMPIRE |author = Ethan Anderton |date = 2011-04-26 |publisher = Collider |language = en |access-date = 2018-08-27 |archive-date = 2020-01-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200105184615/https://collider.com/william-forsythe-charlie-cox-boardwalk-empire/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>、《[[火線警探|火線警探]]》和《{{link-en|無名氏 (電視劇)|John Doe (TV series)|無名氏}}》中飾演常設角色。

